{"tid":2436466,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"恐煩偽：相信事主因中風導致死亡","createTime":"2021-03-07T07:20:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T07:50:07.000Z","uid":64694,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8ee96e8ae3a5dd46c814585e4e9918c7c13075c1","tid":2436466,"uid":64694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T07:20:02.000Z","msg":"女子死前曾接種疫苗 孔繁毅相信事主因中風導致死亡<br />\n<br />\n一名55歲女子昨日出現急性中風，入住廣華醫院，隨後出現心臟停頓，今日清晨不治。根據家屬提供資料，她曾於今個星期二在佐敦官涌體育館社區疫苗接種中心接種科興新冠疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n新冠疫苗臨牀事件評估專家委員會共同召集人孔繁毅表示，死者本身有高血壓、血脂高和蛋白尿等長期病患，相信是中風導致死亡，委員會下星期一會審視死者的解剖報告和相關數據，之後再作交代。<br />\n<br />\n孔繁毅說，暫時未清楚個案與疫苗接種是否有直接關係，也沒有接種疫苗後會引發中風的數據，現階段不會叫停接種計劃，估計對市民接種率不會有影響。他又指，長者和長期病患者是高危感染群組，死亡率為最高，有關群組應要先接種疫苗，委員會亦已審視相關數據，確保60歲或以上人士接種疫苗的安全性。<br />\n<br />\n對於連續有兩名市民在同一個接種中心接種疫苗後死亡，孔繁毅說，相信只是巧合，接種中心的醫護人員不會詳細詢問市民的身體狀況，市民有責任先向醫護交代，又指專家委員會一直強調，長期病患者的病情如果控制得理想，一直有覆診就不會有問題，建議市民在接種疫苗前先諮詢家庭醫生意見。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1579120-20210306.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1579120-20210306.htm&d=nX%2BkuNaC9t4xEeYfS0E7bHbrkFmDP3UEX6OAVSOiSMc%3D&h=a7920e4b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1579120-20210306.htm&h=e95dd82d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1579120-20210306.htm</a>"},{"pid":"dc387057d4af70c563eedb08e57e2a05f7d13ff5","tid":2436466,"uid":10635,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T07:25:24.000Z","msg":"不如學回魂夜， 話比幻覺嚇死好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51b1705b045ba747cb0242c57ae9c217fc01fab5","tid":2436466,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dc387057d4af70c563eedb08e57e2a05f7d13ff5","tid":2436466,"uid":10635,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T07:25:24.000Z","msg":"不如學回魂夜， 話比幻覺嚇死好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T07:27:49.000Z","msg":"咪就係打左毒疫苗中風"},{"pid":"9c0c6c7c62da76e268725965c4c7a484553655f9","tid":2436466,"uid":153239,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T07:27:57.000Z","msg":"信正苦唔戴 可以改成 信正苦唔怕了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14e8430285eb49d8d7d50613aee76984a8f174ab","tid":2436466,"uid":37528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T07:28:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所謂專家vs on9藍屍"},{"pid":"b6f88fa99f4b337439dac1b336e2b64792c8278a","tid":2436466,"uid":364767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T07:32:06.000Z","msg":"即係 打咗 疫苗 先至 中風"},{"pid":"f8b89d90fb13bd51a6c0e40d5c35cdef282dac89","tid":2436466,"uid":299430,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T07:33:30.000Z","msg":"有幾多個老人家冇高血壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c75ef7c079ba4cdef7c20eaefc993369c58fd13a","tid":2436466,"uid":129664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T07:50:07.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">也沒有接種疫苗後會引發中風的數據</span><br />\n咁而家咪第一個囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前冇就代表之後都會冇架咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}